1/By June, 2020, ~ 35K genome sequences of the #SARS_CoV_2 virus (the virus that causes #COVID19) were identified. The #Alpha & #Beta strains were identified as VOCs in December, 2020. Before the Wuhan strain based #COVIDVaccine was 1st administered.
https://t.co/9xes6BMiuo https://t.co/9ZoV1yjam3

2/By the time the general pop was ready to be fully vaccinated with the #CovidVaccine, the #SARSCoV2 virus mutation was already on and poppin'.  The #Delta strain of #COVID19 was present by May, 2021. The USA did not acknowledge Delta until later -> the Provincetown outbreak.
